data.description: Beautiful one level living near parks & schools! This 3 bedroom home offers an inviting living space w/pellet stove, spacious kitchen, oversized pantry space. Home has several updates including: Fresh exterior paint, Heat pump components replaced, New vinyl windows throughout home, Updated water heater, All fencing redone, Newer roof. Landscaped yard includes beautiful rose bushes & covered deck. Two sheds, one drywalled and ready for creative use! MUST SEE!
